<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
</head>
<body>
    <div id="side-bar" class="side-bar">
        <span class="close-btn" onclick="toggleSidebar()">&times;</span>
        <a href="/Home/Index">Home</a>
        <a href="/Riwayat/Index">Riwayat Penyewaan</a>
        <a href="/Contact/Index">Kontak Kami</a>
    </div>
    <div class="nav-bar">
        <div class="left-content">
            <div class="hamburger" onclick="toggleSidebar()">&#9776;</div>
            <div id="Title">RentCar</div>
        </div>
        <div class="right-content">
            @if (string.IsNullOrEmpty(@ViewData["Username"] as string))
            {
                <a href="/Account/Login" class="btn">Login</a>
                <a href="/Account/Register" class="btn">Registrasi</a>
            }
            else
            {
                <h2>Hi, @ViewData["Username"]!</h2>
            }
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="welcome-text">Selamat Datang di Rental Mobil Kami</div>
    <div class="main-content">
        <div class="about-us">
            RentCar, layanan penyewaan mobil terpercaya yang didesain untuk memudahkan perjalanan Anda. Kami menyediakan berbagai pilihan mobil berkualitas
            yang dapat Anda sewa dengan mudah dan cepat melalui platform berbasis web yang inovatif. Di RentCar, kami memahami kebutuhan mobilitas Anda,
            sehingga kami hadir dengan fitur pencarian yang intuitif, histori transaksi yang transparan, serta proses pemesanan yang aman dan sederhana melalui website kami.
        </div>
        <div class="contact-us">
            <h3>Contact Us !</h3>
            <div id="phone-number">(021) 12341234</div>
            <div id="address">Bee Tower, Jl. Setiabudi No.Kav 18 16th Floor, Kuningan, South Jakarta City</div>
        </div>
    </div>
    <footer>
        <div>ⓒ 2024 RentCar App. Semua Hak Dilindungi.</div>
    </footer>
</body>
</html>

<style>
    * {
        margin: 0;
        padding: 0;
        box-sizing: border-box;
    }

    body {
        background-color: #f6f2f7;
        font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
        max-width: 100%;
    }

    /* ----- navbar settings----- */
    .nav-bar {
        background-color: #e5cffe;
        display: flex;
        justify-content: space-between;
        align-items: center;
        padding: 10px;
        top: 0;
        width: 100%;
    }

    .hamburger {
        font-size: 18px;
        cursor: pointer;
        color: #6d597a;
    }

    .side-bar {
        height: 100%;
        width: 250px;
        position: fixed;
        top: 0;
        left: -250px;
        background-color: #6d597a;
        overflow-x: hidden;
        transition: 0.3s;
        padding-top: 60px;
        z-index: 1000;
    }

    .side-bar a {
        padding: 10px 15px;
        text-decoration: none;
        font-size: 20px;
        color: #fff;
        display: block;
        transition: 0.3s;
    }

    .side-bar a:hover {
        background-color: #4e4465;
    }

    .side-bar .close-btn {
        position: absolute;
        top: 10px;
        right: 20px;
        font-size: 30px;
        cursor: pointer;
        color: #fff;
    }

    .side-bar.active {
        left: 0;
    }

    .left-content {
        display: flex;
        align-items: center;
    }

    #Title {
        padding-left: 10px;
        font-weight: bold;
        color: #615c74;
    }

    .right-content {
        display: flex;
        gap: 10px;
    }

    .right-content .btn {
        display: inline-block;
        padding: 10px 20px;
        background-color: #ff9999;
        color: white;
        text-decoration: none;
        border-radius: 3px;
        border: none;
        cursor: pointer;
    }

    .right-content .btn:hover {
        background-color: #ff6666;
    }

    .right-content h2 {
        font-size: 15px;
        font-weight: 100;
    }

    /* ----- main content settings----- */
    .welcome-text {
        font-weight: bold;
        color: #615c74;
        font-size: 25px;
        text-align: center;
        padding-top: 40px;
        padding-bottom: 20px;
    }

    .main-content {
        display: flex;
        justify-content: center;
        align-items: center;
        gap: 60px;
        margin: 0 auto;
        margin-top: 40px;
        margin-bottom: 40px;
        align-items: center;
    }

    .about-us {
        max-width: 450px;
        text-align: justify;
    }

    .contact-us {
        max-width: 450px;
    }
    .contact-us h3{
        text-align: center;
        padding-bottom: 10px;
    }
    .contact-us #phone-number {
            color: #ff9999;
    }
    
    /* ----- footer settings----- */
    footer {
        background-color: #e5cffe;
        text-align: center;
        padding: 15px;
        font-size: 10px;
        margin-top: 30px;
    }
</style>

<script>
    setTimeout(function () {
        location.reload();
    }, 600000);

    function toggleSidebar() {
        var sidebar = document.getElementById("side-bar");
        sidebar.classList.toggle("active");
    }

    function redirectToSearch() {
        window.location.href = "http://localhost:5175/Car/index";
    }
</script>